Ting Wei je alergický na psie a mačacie chlpy.

280
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,880
Prepáčte.

281
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,930
To nič.

282
00:20:05,150 --> 00:20:07,890
