Auto je tu.

292
00:20:47,690 --> 00:20:50,820
Ostatní, odchádzam teraz s Tao Le Si.

293
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:53,150
Lu Tian Xing,

294
00:20:53,150 --> 00:20:54,460
