335
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,420
Tak vieš, kam chodí?

336
00:23:32,730 --> 00:23:34,540
Neviem.

337
00:23:35,910 --> 00:23:39,290
Aj keby mi zdvihol, nepovedal by mi to.

