683
00:53:33,790 --> 00:53:37,600
Máš niekoho rada? A Tian Xing o tom vie?

684
00:53:38,570 --> 00:53:40,330
Vie.

685
00:53:47,680 --> 00:53:51,040
Vie, že máš niekoho rada,

686
00:53:51,040 --> 00:53:53,800
