Idem naspäť.

818
01:06:50,160 --> 01:06:52,070
Dobre.

819
01:06:52,070 --> 01:06:54,410
Prepáč.

820
01:06:54,410 --> 01:06:57,010
Môžem sa ospravedlniť?

821
01:06:57,010 --> 01:07:00,150
