01:09:44,860 --> 01:09:47,370
Prší, vypadnime odtiaľto, dobre?

844
01:09:51,360 --> 01:09:53,290
Ochorieš.

845
01:09:54,190 --> 01:09:55,830
Poďme.

846
01:09:55,830 --> 01:09:57,200
Nestaraj sa o mňa.

847
01:09:57,200 --> 01:10:00,320
Akože sa o teba nemám starať? Veď leje!

848
01:10:00,320 --> 01:10:02,180
Nenič sa takto, dobre?

849
01:10:02,960 --> 01:10:04,470
Bojím sa o teba.

850
01:10:04,470 --> 01:10:06,770
Nepotrebujem, aby si sa o mňa bál.

851
01:10:06,770 --> 01:10:08,760
